subject: New poll for junit
msgSnippet: Enter your vote today!  A new poll has been created for the junit group: JUNIT was introduced in your company. What effect did it have on the project duration
messageBody:
Enter your vote today! A new poll has been created for the
junit group:

JUNIT was introduced in your company.
What effect did it have on the project
duration ?

o longer duration (with better quality)
o no change in duration
o reduction of duration
o benefit after first attempt


To vote, please visit the following web page:

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/junit/polls

Note: Please do not reply to this message. Poll votes are
not collected via email. To vote, you must go to the Yahoo! Groups
web site listed above.

Thanks!
